1. click on create button.
2. Upload images in images section using upload button.
3. Enter text with respect to images and click on "upload Your Text". To covert your text into a mp3 audio file.
4. After all this proccess click on  "Add Frame to genrate the video from uploaded images and mp3 file.
5. Now you also upload video using in video upload section.
6. After creating multiple video using multiple image and audio file click on "Merge video" to merge all the videos in a single presentation.
7. If you want to delete video from presentation click on "Delete" button.
8. Click on "Finish" button to warp up the project.  



**  Note: if you are uploading images first then given some text with respect to those images. Don't upload the video in between this proccess.